00:02:36.976 --> 00:02:40.696
The head of CACI made $20,000,000.

53
00:02:40.696 --> 00:02:42.456
Those are things I had no idea about

54
00:02:42.456 --> 00:02:46.256
and I was troubled and shocked and it was painful

55
00:02:46.256 --> 00:02:48.826
because people's lives are being lost.

56
00:02:48.826 --> 00:02:52.192
<v Regina>We're not just talking about mercenaries.</v>

57
00:02:52.192 --> 00:02:55.248
I think, even when the war first began, there were stories

