00:02:55.248 --> 00:02:58.428
about people who went over in a more mercenary fashion,

59
00:02:58.428 --> 00:03:01.108
you know, bold men to make a profit,

60
00:03:01.108 --> 00:03:02.848
knowing what they were getting into.

61
00:03:02.848 --> 00:03:06.528
This is not exactly what we're talking about here, is it?

62
00:03:06.528 --> 00:03:08.608
<v ->No, what we're focused on in the movie</v>

63
00:03:08.608 --> 00:03:12.388
is the corporations, the boards of directors,

64
00:03:12.388 --> 00:03:17.328
the heads of the corporations, who are leading the charge

65
00:03:17.328 --> 00:03:20.900
to profit from the war at the very same time

66
00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:25.760
that men and women, Americans, Iraqis, children

67
00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:29.060
are being killed and hospitals are not being built,

68
00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:31.660
these companies are taking hundreds of millions

69
00:03:31.660 --> 00:03:35.620
and literally billions of dollars out of Iraq

70
00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:38.480
and into their private coffers.

71
00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:41.019
That's wrong and there's been no discussion of it.

72
00:03:41.019 --> 00:03:43.020
<v Regina>Right, very little discussion</v>

