Specifics, a couple specifics?

77
00:03:56.312 --> 00:03:58.352
<v ->There's a truck driver in the movie.</v>

78
00:03:58.352 --> 00:03:59.912
A guy I just love, I haven't met him,

79
00:03:59.912 --> 00:04:02.212
it's just been on the phone, named Shane,

80
00:04:02.212 --> 00:04:06.832
and he talks about going over there to help his family,

81
00:04:06.832 --> 00:04:11.712
to do the right thing, to rebuild Iraq, to help the troops,

82
00:04:11.712 --> 00:04:13.733
goes to work for Halliburton, truck driver,

83
00:04:13.733 --> 00:04:17.032
just driving a truck in some city in the United States.

84
00:04:17.032 --> 00:04:18.772
<v Regina>He thinks he's part of the good effort.</v>

85
00:04:18.772 --> 00:04:22.632
<v ->Yeah, and he gets over there and he discovers that,</v>

86
00:04:22.632 --> 00:04:24.834
and I didn't believe this when I first heard it,

87
00:04:25.984 --> 00:04:29.092
Halliburton's charging you and everybody watching this

