00:04:29.092 --> 00:04:33.778
cause it's out tax dollars, $45 for a six-pack of Coke.

89
00:04:34.788 --> 00:04:36.084
<v Regina>You are kidding...</v>

90
00:04:36.084 --> 00:04:39.724
I've heard of these exorbitant prices, $45 for a six-pack?

91
00:04:39.724 --> 00:04:41.884
<v ->Right, and we heard that over and over and over again</v>

92
00:04:41.884 --> 00:04:46.560
and then, a soldier and several other Halliburton

93
00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:48.255
truck drivers talk about setting

94
00:04:48.255 --> 00:04:52.791
their laundry out, t-shirts, underwear, $100.

95
00:04:52.791 --> 00:04:56.471
Now, all of that comes out of your pocket because these

96
00:04:56.471 --> 00:05:01.441
contracts are what's called cost-plus contracts, it means--

97
00:05:01.441 --> 00:05:02.807
<v Regina>What's that mean cost-plus--</v>

98
00:05:02.807 --> 00:05:03.890
<v ->Well, that's what I'm--
