00:06:58.687 --> 00:07:00.048
what part of the country it is,

142
00:07:00.048 --> 00:07:03.687
but the things that the soldiers told me over and over again

143
00:07:03.687 --> 00:07:06.465
is that they would be working right next to somebody,

144
00:07:06.465 --> 00:07:09.986
who would be doing exactly the same job as the soldier,

145
00:07:09.986 --> 00:07:11.023
and that person would be getting

146
00:07:11.023 --> 00:07:14.562
three and four times what the soldier made,

147
00:07:14.562 --> 00:07:17.903
and again, your tax dollars are paying for that.

148
00:07:17.903 --> 00:07:19.162
<v Regina>So it's a significant amount</v>

149
00:07:19.162 --> 00:07:20.742
of money to be a truck driver.

150
00:07:20.742 --> 00:07:22.671
<v ->Oh yeah, yes.</v>

151
00:07:22.671 --> 00:07:26.733
<v Regina>They're tempted into going over for all the</v>

