00:07:55.864 --> 00:07:59.705
that had been closed, that had been marked dangerous,

163
00:07:59.705 --> 00:08:02.054
but Halliburton pushed it because

164
00:08:02.054 --> 00:08:03.942
they get paid by the number of trips,

165
00:08:03.942 --> 00:08:06.643
by they way, they don't have to deliver anything.

166
00:08:06.643 --> 00:08:09.580
They just have to take trips so we even had truck drivers

