00:08:09.580 --> 00:08:13.440
tell us about driving, virtually, empty trucks across Iraq

168
00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:16.340
because the billing procedure awards Halliburton for that.

169
00:08:16.340 --> 00:08:17.380
<v Regina>That's criminal.</v>

170
00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:20.214
<v ->Yeah, and in this particular case, "Friday Massacre",</v>

171
00:08:20.214 --> 00:08:24.494
we have the two women whose husbands were killed

172
00:08:24.494 --> 00:08:28.212
in that massacre because Halliburton did not abide

173
00:08:28.212 --> 00:08:32.992
by any kind of safety rules or regulations

174
00:08:32.992 --> 00:08:34.512
and there was no protection or

